'From Squeak2.7 of 5 January 2000 [latest update: #1789] on 5 February 2000 at 3:38:11 pm'!"Change Set:		FasterMVCDisplay-hmmDate:			5 January 2000Author:			Hans-Martin MosnerSpeeds up whole-window displaying, resizing and moving in MVC. Actual improvement depends a bit on your graphics performance."!!ControlManager methodsFor: 'displaying' stamp: 'hmm 1/5/2000 07:00'!restore: aRectangle	"Restore all windows visible in aRectangle"	^ self restore: aRectangle without: nil! !!ControlManager methodsFor: 'displaying' stamp: 'hmm 12/30/1999 19:35'!restore: aRectangle without: aView	"Restore all windows visible in aRectangle"	Display deferUpdates: true.	self restore: aRectangle below: 1 without: aView.	Display deferUpdates: false; forceToScreen: aRectangle! !!StandardSystemView methodsFor: 'displaying' stamp: 'hmm 7/21/1999 07:37'!displayDeEmphasized 	"Display this view with emphasis off.	If windowBits is not nil, then simply BLT if possible,		but force full display for top window so color is preserved."	(bitsValid and: [controller ~~ ScheduledControllers activeController])		ifTrue: [self lock.				windowBits displayAt: self windowOrigin]		ifFalse: [Display deferUpdates: true.				super display.				Display deferUpdates: false; forceToScreen: self windowBox.				CacheBits ifTrue: [self cacheBitsAsIs]]! !